{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_14_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？\n私が恋愛ゲームのヒロインに？",
      "startTime": 1.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今度のもし恋は『大人の恋愛』がテーマなので\nぜひ、莉央さんにお願いしたいそうです",
      "startTime": 9.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "大人の恋愛……それで年長組の私にオファーがきたのね\nでも、私との恋愛なんて需要があるのかしら？",
      "startTime": 18.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "需要とか言わないで下さい。莉央さんのファンは大勢\nいますから、中には恋愛したい人もきっといますよ",
      "startTime": 26.5666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "「中には」とか「きっと」とか、一言余計よ",
      "startTime": 30.2999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0999989192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、もし恋の魅力は恋のトキメキや青春のキラキラ\nでしょ？　私のイメージには合わないと思うけど",
      "startTime": 39.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。トキメキや青春とは馴染みがなくても\n莉央さんには莉央さんの良さがあります",
      "startTime": 47.1999989192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8333322525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから微妙に褒められてる気がしないのよね……\nまぁ、恋愛に馴染みがないのは認めるけど",
      "startTime": 54.2234722842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんだって\n私と恋愛なんて考えられないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 59.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……そうですね",
      "startTime": 62.0666655858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8666655858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですねじゃないでしょ。そこはお世辞でも\n「そんなことありません」と言うところでしょ",
      "startTime": 68.6249125395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6666635513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……まぁいいわ\nこれも仕事だと思って割り切ってやるわよ",
      "startTime": 74.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。では、次の打ち合わせまでに\nアンケートに回答しておいてもらえますか",
      "startTime": 81.9999943415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.6333276748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "確か、恋愛に関するアンケートを取って\n私の理想の恋愛像をゲームに反映するのよね？",
      "startTime": 87.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、恋愛とは無縁な私にアンケートを取っても\n面白い答えなんて出ないわよ",
      "startTime": 96.1999943415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.6999943415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに無縁は言い過ぎじゃないですか？\n莉央さんほどの美人なら学生時代はモテたでしょう",
      "startTime": 102.3666610081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9666610099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "中学では陸上部と生徒会長を掛け持ち\n高校ではアイドル活動。恋愛する暇なんてなかったわ",
      "startTime": 109.6999943415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "だから私に恋愛の話を期待されても……\nまぁいいわ。アンケートは適当に書いておくから",
      "startTime": 118.4333256403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.599990781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛ゲームに興味はないけど\n仕事はちゃんとやるから、後は任せてちょうだい",
      "startTime": 125.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 129.4666574477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 130.5999887346
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 130.5999887346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、今日のライブの後、時間を取ってくれる？\nアンケートのことで相談に乗ってほしいんだけど",
      "startTime": 136.3999887465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 139.4332986831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "私なりにアンケートを書いてみたけど、恋のトキメキが\n足りない気がして……貴方の意見を聞かせてほしいの",
      "startTime": 143.1999887465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 147.7332935969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは構いませんが、あまり乗り気じゃなかったのに\n急に前向きになるなんて、何かあったんですか？",
      "startTime": 151.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 155.0666269302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと事情があって、誰もが私と結婚したくなる\n至高の恋愛ゲームを作らなければいけなくなったのよ",
      "startTime": 158.7999836603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "言ってることがよく分からないんですが……\nどういう事情か、詳しく教えてもらえませんか？",
      "startTime": 165.1691968645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 168.9332935969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "……昨日発売された雑誌で、アイドルを\nランキング付けする読者投票企画をやっていたの",
      "startTime": 171.7999836603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "その中に『お嫁さんにしたいアイドルランキング』\nという項目があって……",
      "startTime": 179.0666595459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そのランキング企画は以前もやっていましたよね\n確か莉央さんは第一回が30位で第二回は2位……",
      "startTime": 184.8333119074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 189.7332885106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、前は2位だった私が、今回は……\nランク外に落ちていたのよ！",
      "startTime": 194.999978574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなは軒並み上位で、リズノワの他の三人\nですらランキング入りしてたのに！　私だけが……",
      "startTime": 201.6623313148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 205.4332885106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんですか\nでも、そんなことはあまり気にしなくても……",
      "startTime": 207.699978574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
